               <p>JOHN WARD. I live at <placeName id="t18091206-26-crimeloc153">No. 4, Henrietta-street, Manchester-square</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18091206-26-crimeloc153" type="placeName" value="No. 4, Henrietta-street, Manchester-square"></interp>
