                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18091206-26-off151 t18091206-26-crimeloc153"></join>. On Sunday, the 25th of June last, I went to bed at night and put my watch in my hat, under the bed; the prisoner laid with me. On Monday morning, about five o'clock, he asked me to tell him what o'clock it was; I looked for my watch in my hat, it was gone.</p>
